        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:3:14:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/14/1",
        "text": [
          ": \"إِذَا تَزَوَّجَ اَلرَّجُلُ اَلْمَرْأَةَ لِمَالِهَا أَوْ جَمَالِهَا لَمْ يُرْزَقْ ذَلِكَ فَإِنْ تَزَوَّجَهَا لِدِينِهَا رَزَقَهُ اَللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ جَمَالَهَا وَ مَالَهَا \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.4380 - Hisham ibn al-Hakam narrated from Abu Abdillah (as) who said: \"If a man marries a woman for her wealth or her beauty, he will not be granted that. But if he marries her for her religion, Allah (swt), the Almighty and Glorious, will grant him her beauty and her wealth.\""
          ]
        }
      }
